&lt;li&gt;You can design experiments, reason about causality, and identify when a correlation is enough and when it is not&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are comfortable owning ambiguous, open-ended problems and breaking them down into a credible plan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You communicate findings crisply to technical and non-technical audiences, in writing, in dashboards, and in person&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You raise the bar for the team through code review, methodology review, and mentorship of less senior analysts and scientists&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
